[size=4][b]The things Stardew Valley breaks for custom (mod) languages on PC — fixed.[/b][/size]

If you play with a community translation (a custom «mod» language), a few things quietly break on the desktop game. This mod fixes all three. It works with [b]any[/b] language pack; with a built-in game language it does nothing at all.

[line]

[size=4][b]What it fixes[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][b]Junimo bundle names — immediately.[/b] Community Center bundle names stay English until you save, quit to the title screen and reload, because the game caches Data/Bundles in English before your language is applied. They're now localized as soon as the save loads. [b]Your bundle progress is never touched[/b] — only display names are refreshed, so remixed bundles and completion are safe.
[*][b]Social page: single male farmers.[/b] In gendered languages the social page showed single [b]male[/b] farmers (your own character, co-op farmhands) with the [b]feminine[/b] single status. It's a first-party game bug — the farmer slot only ever reads the female status key and splits it, so a pack with separate male/female strings gets the female form for men. Each farmer now shows the correct gendered status.
[*][b]Localized «(Recipe)» suffix.[/b] For Ukrainian packs only: the game uses one «(Recipe)» key for both cooking recipes and crafting blueprints, which Ukrainian has to tell apart. Food gets «(Рецепт)», everything else «(Креслення)». Other languages are unaffected.
[/list]

[line]

[size=4][b]Requirements[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][b]SMAPI[/b] 4.0 or newer.
[*][b]A language pack[/b] — any custom language mod. With a built-in game language this mod does nothing.
[/list]

[size=4][b]Installation[/b][/size]

Unzip into your [b]Mods[/b] folder and run the game through SMAPI. Everything is on by default; the three toggles live in [b]config.json[/b] if you ever hit a conflict with another mod.

[i]On Android?[/i] Use «Custom Language Fixes» instead — it includes these fixes plus everything else the mobile port breaks for custom languages.

[line]

Source code and full technical write-up: [url=https://github.com/ThatHunky/CustomLanguageFixes]github.com/ThatHunky/CustomLanguageFixes[/url]. Licensed MIT.

Credits: [b]Pereclaw[/b] for the Ukrainian translation this was diagnosed against, and [b]DID[/b] for testing.

[line]

[size=4][b]Українською[/b][/size]

Три речі, які гра ламає для кастомних (мод-) мов на ПК — виправлено:
[list]
[*]назви клунків Джунімо одразу після завантаження сейва, без ритуалу «збережись, вийди в меню, зайди знову» (прогрес клунків не зачіпається);
[*]правильний за статтю статус «самотній» на слоті фермера — чоловічі фермери більше не показують «незаміжня» (ванільний баг гри);
[*]суфікс «(Рецепт)»/«(Креслення)» для українських паків — гра не розрізняє їжу від креслень, а мод розрізняє.
[/list]

Потрібні SMAPI 4.0+ і будь-який мовний пак. Усе ввімкнено за замовчуванням; вимикачі — у config.json.
